  "text": "Using as an example a fifth-density group or social memory complex of the Orion group, what was their previous density before they became fifth density? I am Ra. The progress through densities is sequential. A fifth-density social memory complex would be comprised of mind/body/spirit complexes harvested from fourth density. Then the conglomerate or mass mind/body/spirit complex does its melding and the results are due to the infinitely various possibilities of combination of distortions.",
